        "en": "The umbrella was hooked on the outside of the fence.Just beyond the parking lot is a shared bicycle and pedestrian path.Why was it placed on the outside?If it was to free one’s hands while parking, placing it inside would seem more natural.\nAccess to the parking lot requires unlocking the entrance gate with a key.It is therefore possible that the umbrella was hung there temporarily while unlocking it.However, the location is about three meters away from the entrance.\nConsidering this, that explanation also seems unlikely."
